            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "A fluttering bird, a shouting merchant, or even a shiny pebble can pull this character\u2019s focus mid-shot, sending arrows veering into the void. They\u2019ll stop to admire a cloud while nocking an arrow, forgetting the target entirely. Archery contests are a lost cause\u2014they\u2019re too busy daydreaming. Concentration is their eternal foe.",
